Compound of {{compound|ja|sort=はららご|はらら|tr1=harara|t1=[[separately]] and in an [[unorderly]] fashion|pos1=adverb|子|tr2=ko|t2=small thing}}.<ref name="KDJ2">{{R:Nihon Kokugo Daijiten 2}}</ref><ref name="DJS">{{R:Daijisen}}</ref><ref name="DJR"/> {{rendaku2|sort=はららご|ko|go}}

First attested in 1578.<ref name="KDJ2"/>

The specific {{m|en|[[salmon]] [[roe]]}} sense has been largely replaced by the term {{ja-r|イクラ}} since the latter term's introduction in the mid-1920s.<ref name="KDJ2-ikura">{{R:Nihon Kokugo Daijiten 2|イクラ}}</ref>

